Description

Mayor Vincent R. Impellitteri escorts His Majesty King Faisal II Al-Hashimi of Iraq to the city hall for the ceremony of presentation of the Medal of Honor of New York City. From photograph album, "Visit of his Majesty the King of Iraq and his Royal Highness the Regent of Iraq to the United States of America, August 12 to September 8, 1952."
